# Eval Feedback Template

Use this file to provide qualitative feedback on eval results.
After each eval run, review the failures and note:
1. Whether the failure is a **skill bug** (script doesn't work correctly)
2. Whether the failure is an **eval bug** (expected output is wrong)
3. Whether the failure is a **fixture bug** (mock state doesn't match reality)

